{"tid":1786803,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［抵制英皇］新假期幫元氣賣廣告","createTime":"2019-12-17T12:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T06:32:16.000Z","uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1c73e48b5fb73ad7abc807d73a2686f87458dfd5","tid":1786803,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s7p4vE6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs7p4vE6.png&h=542e9128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聖誕節緊係食火雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有雞唔食走去叫讀者食蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fogiz7p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffogiz7p.png&h=058773d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說iSqaure開咗英皇戲院，唔該唔好幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vxk3MeX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVxk3MeX.png&h=0426d697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羊生個仔係北京政協<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">釋放容祖兒！</span><span style=\"color: green;\">釋放張敬軒！</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">釋放蔡卓妍！</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">釋放鍾欣桐！</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">釋放古巨基！</span><span style=\"color: teal;\">釋放關智斌！</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">釋放鍾舒漫！</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">釋放洪卓立！</span><span style=\"color: maroon;\">釋放許靖韻！</span>釋放香港人！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8NB6J3W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8NB6J3W.jpg&h=571a4ad0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（曾樂彤就唔洗釋放啦，留返你地慢慢嘆）"},{"pid":"a8d56d69e9a75964a16f9009ecf7a